entries.s_11: More fodder? You must be out of traitors by now.
entries.s_12: These men, whatever their allegiance, are no longer of any interest to me.
entries.s_4: You have become quite bothersome. Unfortunately for you only I have the key to this gate.
entries.s_6: Step away from the holo-projector and we can discuss it further.
entries.s_8: I have no need to fight you. Once we arrive at our destination I will have this entire level vented of atmosphere. For now I have alterted Watch Captain to your presence. Soon enough you will cease to be my problem.
